name: 丹尼尔·奈迈施
name_full: 丹尼尔·奈迈施 Daniel Nemes
introduction: Daniel is a theatre, film and television actor. Born in Sydney, Australia. He worked extensively in theatre before transitioning into film and television, appearing in Australian television shows Home & Away and Packed To The Rafters. He has appeared alongside Alyson Hannigan in Abducted: The Mary Stauffer Story and Academy Award Winner, Marlee Matlin in The Magicians. He has studied at the world renowned Ivana Chubbuck Studios and Groundlings in addition to many other amazing coaches.
